Interface IHandleBrokerMessage

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BrokerManager

    public interface IHandleBrokerMessage
    There may be multiple swaps coming in. Each has its own ID. If a client is already engaged in a swap, then subsequent swaps are denied immediately.
